Edit the script and set your target:
CAMERA_IP="192.168.1.100"   # Target camera IP  
CAMERA_PORT="554"           # Default RTSP port is 554  
INTERFACE="eth0"            # Network interface (optional, leave blank for IPv4)  

Run the script: 
./rtsp_bruteforce.sh

Example Output: 
