  Passwords: /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt
  Interface: eth0
  Paths: stream1 h264 live.sdp videoMain ...
------------------------------------
Testing rtsp://admin:12345@[192.168.1.100%eth0]:554/stream1 ...
